    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/27aec953a789d79a82eb9cf77f54231b.poster.avif?t=1770048446\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/27aec953a789d79a82eb9cf77f54231b.webm?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/27aec953a789d79a82eb9cf77f54231b.mp4?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《倾听画语》就像是一本生动的小说、一部可互动的电影，讲述一位追逐梦想的画家，为了完成心目中的完美作品，不曾停下她的画笔。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/dcf5768d9bbf83d2ae1e19ba0dcd31c4.poster.avif?t=1770048446\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/dcf5768d9bbf83d2ae1e19ba0dcd31c4.webm?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/dcf5768d9bbf83d2ae1e19ba0dcd31c4.mp4?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你将扮演一名追逐梦想的画家，找寻那些使你的画作鲜活却已遗失的色彩。只有在偶尔休息片刻时，来杯咖啡和早餐让你提振精神继续创作。藉由创作的每一幅绘画作品，感受其中述说的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/3ee2c3f05daa463f9e0aa8c8fd2f7b38.poster.avif?t=1770048446\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/3ee2c3f05daa463f9e0aa8c8fd2f7b38.webm?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/3ee2c3f05daa463f9e0aa8c8fd2f7b38.mp4?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>透过点击与拖曳，你能以随心所欲的步调尽情享受轻鬆、扣人心弦的游戏体验。并在流畅悠扬的配乐下，沉浸于充满绚烂色彩与精緻逐格动画的全景世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/c9530a69ba2e627224fb3740aa57408c.poster.avif?t=1770048446\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/c9530a69ba2e627224fb3740aa57408c.webm?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/c9530a69ba2e627224fb3740aa57408c.mp4?t=1770048446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
